line_2: Many who feel, and more who fear the stroke.

line_1: Wild to get loose, his Patience I provoke,
line_2: Mistake, confound, object, at all he spoke.

line_1: Display the Times, High-Church or Low provoke;
line_2: We'll praise the Weapon, as we like the Stroke,

line_1: What rapture does my soul provoke?
line_2: What Genius points to yonder oak?

line_1: Or did to fight your valiant bands provoke;
line_2: That 'gainst his will the treaties sworn, he broke,

line_1: Did never me as yet provoke,
line_2: Either to honour band and cloak,

line_2: Or deck my hat with leaves of oak.

line_1: Big-swoln with folly, as her smiles provoke,

line_1: And Israel did his Rage so far provoke,
line_2: That what the God-head wrote, the Prophet broke.

line_1: Whose lashes soon the mules provoke;
line_2: Much more, the Lord Alphonso spoke;
Read how he thought, and what he spoke.
In thunder to the passions spoke!
